column5: Soon bro! Just getting settled this sem.
Did you see the match last night?
Planning a trip to Goa in May. You in?
Maybe. Need to check my finances later.
Sent you a funny reel. Check it.
Sorry! My notifications are a mess.
I'm coming to your city Saturday. Beer?
Can't this weekend. Got a concert and some family stuff.
Saw you at the concert! Tried to wave but you were with a girl.
Oh really? Didn't see you. It was crowded.
You've changed man. Hardly talk anymore.
Just growing up I guess. Talk soon.
